                                                    Linux Basic Command


=>For root
$sudo
=>For Update 
$ sudu apt update
=>For stop any command 
$ control+c
=>To check Password 
$ su
=>For Clear screen
$ clear
=>To update system 
$ sudo upgrade
=>To check IP of kali linux
$ ifconfig
=>To check version of any pkg
e.g   $ nmap  --version
=>To check port is active or not 
$ netstate  --tulnp
=>To change directory or move to folder 
$ cd /apt
=>To move back from a folder
$ cd ..

=>To see folders inside kali linux
$ ls
=>To check main user or folder
$ whoami
=>To check detail of system
$ uname  -a
=>To remove file
$ nano file name





